=head1 NAME

Regex::Cursor - Regex Cursor nodes

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This file implements the Regex::Cursor class, used for managing regular
expression control flow.  Regex::Cursor is also a base class for
grammars.

=cut

.include 'cclass.pasm'
.include 'src/Regex/constants.pir'

